The '''Southern Wastes''' were an area on the [[Ubese/Legends|Ubese]] homeworld, [[Uba IV/Legends|Uba IV]]. Presumably, they were wastelands formed after the planet was bombarded during the [[bombardment of the Uba system]].

Circa [[3 ABY/Legends|3 ABY]], it was home to several Ubese clans, including [[Clan-Vorsazg]], a clan led by [[War-Master]] [[Savax]]. These clans, possibly with [[Hutt/Legends|Hutt]] assistance, manned a flotilla of [[Capital ship/Legends|capital ships]] to attack the ''[[yrak pootzck]]'' Ubese of [[Ubertica]]. They managed to lay waste to several Ubertican cities before being destroyed by [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] forces.

